# 5 Ways to Increase Table Turnover

Learn proven strategies that helped The Oasis Lounge increase table turnover by 22% while maintaining customer satisfaction.

## Strategy 1: Optimize Session Timing
- Set clear session duration expectations
- Use automated timers to track sessions
- Offer session extensions proactively
- Streamline checkout process

## Strategy 2: Streamline Staff Workflows
- Automate prep notifications
- Reduce wait times between sessions
- Optimize BOH/FOH coordination
- Use real-time status updates

## Strategy 3: Reduce Wait Times
- Pre-prep common flavor combinations
- Optimize table preparation process
- Use predictive analytics for demand
- Implement smart scheduling

## Strategy 4: Improve Table Preparation Efficiency
- Standardize setup procedures
- Use checklists for consistency
- Train staff on best practices
- Monitor preparation times

## Strategy 5: Maximize Revenue Per Table
- Implement dynamic pricing
- Offer session upgrades
- Encourage add-ons and extras
- Optimize flavor pricing

